    "note": "Ace2N-mNeon is an eFRET sensor whose fluorescent reporter is mNeonGreen (the Ace2 opsin is the dark FRET acceptor that quenches it voltage-dependently). The stored excitation/emission arrays are the FPbase mNeonGreen curve verbatim (corr 1.0, max diff 0.0; peaks ex 504 / em 517). No separately measured Ace2N-mNeon ex/em curve is published, so mNeonGreen is the correct displayed fluorophore; source attribution was previously missing.",
